1.Page Load - Test that the inventory page loads successfully and all elements on the page are visible.
    1.Navigate to the inventory page
    2.Verify that all elements such as product images, product names, and prices are visible and displayed correctly.
2.Product Sorting - Test that the product sorting feature works correctly.
    1.Click on the "Sort" drop-down menu and select a sorting option - Price (low to high).
    2.Verify that the products are sorted correctly according to the selected option.
    3.Click on the "Sort" drop-down menu and select a sorting option - Price (high to low).
    4.Verify that the products are sorted correctly according to the selected option.
    5.Click on the "Sort" drop-down menu and select a sorting option - Name (Z to A).
    6.Verify that the products are sorted correctly according to the selected option.
    7.Click on the "Sort" drop-down menu and select a sorting option - Name (A to Z).
    8.Verify that the products are sorted correctly according to the selected option.
3.Product Details - Test that the product details page loads correctly and displays all relevant information about the product.
    1.Click on a product name or image to go to the product details page
    2.Verify that all relevant product information such as name, description, price, and image are displayed correctly.
4.Add to Cart - Test that the "Add to Cart" button works correctly and adds the selected product to the shopping cart.
    1.Click on the "Add to Cart" button for a product
    2.Verify that the selected product is added to the shopping cart and the cart icon in the top right corner of the page is updated to reflect the number of items in the cart.
5.Remove from Cart - Test that the "Remove" button works correctly and removes the selected product from the shopping cart.
    1. Click on the "Remove" button for a product.
    2. Verify that the selected product is removed from the shopping cart and the cart icon in the top right corner of the page is updated to reflect the number of items in the cart.
6. Check that left side menu is opened
    1. Click on the Menu button.
    2. Verify that item list is displayed.
7. All items link - Check that user returns to the Main page from other pages.
    1. Click on a item - Details page is displayed.
    2. Click on Menu button.
    3. Click on the All items. - The main page is displayed.
    4. Click on the cart button.
    5. Click on Menu button.
    6. Click on the All items. - The main page is displayed.
8. About - Check that user redirected to the https://saucelabs.com site
    1. Click on the Menu button.
    2. Click on About button.
